description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Anurak purrs with a rating of 63, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 126, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Stringalong for East, Leverage for South, and Nine Lives for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20632-17693-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [126 Votes, Top 15% Score]
